y can help\ndevelopers understand how vulnerabilitiesoriginate and fix under the\ninteractions of software developers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Jul 2019 21:02:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
